This is


1. execute perlGlue.pl

   this will return a file called test.py.

2. add code of extractVelocity.py into the test.py as a "head"

   this will create a whole package to extract the velocity field you are interested in.

then upload test.py as your script to a server to extract your data


   For example:

      $ pvpython test.py

## function explaination

1. extractVelocity.py file

   Specify the location of your case file that includes .foam

2. perlGlue.pl

   Specify the location of the sampling line to generate the velocity fild.

  ==> line 17&18 change the line coodinates

  ==> line 23 change the saving file path